column6: Indonesia;1.0;"I visited your place today with my brother. While he was ordering coffee

column9: cut-open wire from those lights shocked me.

column2: and my right leg cramped and went numb. What really surprised me
column4: was how the staff handled it. When I told them what happened
column8: ” without even asking if I was okay or showing much concern. Then they just taped a tissue napkin over the wire. That felt careless and unsafe

column10: even a child or an elderly person.
